Class TextFormatVectorizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dkpro.core.api.embeddings.text.TextFormatVectorizer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Vectorizer

    public class TextFormatVectorizer
extends Object
implements Vectorizer
    A Vectorizer backed by a Map<String, float[].

    Use load(File) to initialize.
